flowchart LR
    subgraph Init[Initialization]
        Start[Boot and enable DMA1/ADC clocks]
        Regulator[Power ADC regulator; enable TS and VREFINT]
        Calibrate[Run ADC self-calibration]
        Configure[Configure DMA Ch1 and CH17, CH0 scan]
        StartADC[Start continuous ADC conversion]
        Start --> Regulator --> Calibrate --> Configure --> StartADC
    end

    subgraph Runtime[Runtime data path]
        Buffer[DMA circular buffer: 16 two-sample pairs]
        Average[Average raw temperature and VREFINT]
        Vdda[Estimate VDDA from VREFINT calibration]
        Temp[Normalize sensor code and interpolate]
        Outputs[Update display and UART telemetry]
        Buffer --> Average --> Vdda --> Temp --> Outputs
    end

    subgraph FaultPath[Fault path]
        Faults[ADC overrun or DMA transfer error]
    end

    StartADC --> Buffer
    StartADC -. interrupt/error path .-> Faults
    Faults --> Outputs
